fr.cnrs.iees.properties

Interface PropertyListSetters

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataEdge, DataNode, DataTreeNode, ExtendablePropertyList, SimplePropertyList, SimpleWriteProtectablePropertyList
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompoundPropertyListImpl, DataEdgeImpl, DataNodeImpl, DataTreeNodeImpl, ExtendablePropertyListImpl, SharedPropertyListImpl, SharedWriteProtectablePropertyListImpl, SimplePropertyListImpl

    public interface PropertyListSetters
    This interface isolates the generic setters for properties. Most descendants will probably need to also implement PropertyListGetters.
    Author:
    J. Gignoux - 13 f√©vr. 2017
